- Description: it's an app to publish your store, company, or a business, other users can see your store, and buy a service or a product, then, 
this app has two types of users, client and seller



-client: can buy a product or service, cancel tbe product or service, putue it, add it on a shopping cart.
         shopping history.
        
-seller: can add N number of stores in it's profile, can add N number of products and services, to edite them or delete them.
         cann edit the status of a product (released, finished, in comming or canceled), and can hidd X producto of it's inventory
         sales history
         
both users: can search stores on home page (there are all of sotres) by name, city, type or street, to buy products or services, to save them on a 
              shopping car, they also can search products and services by type or name, to comment into the page of each product, and other users
              can respond.

Main pages: Home, Directory, shopping cart, user profile. 
